VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'bringing. So I didn\'t use any fancy prompting. I told it exactly what I wanted to and now I\'m going to click generate and it\'s going to go to work. As with most agent-based creative tools, it will keep you up to date on what\'s going on here. You can see here it\'s'

[02:32] [scene:talk]
